ZH: 这家公司的发展一直是以市场需求为导向的。
EN: The development of this company has always been market-driven.

ZH: 没有一个成功的项目是自己导向的，都是围绕着用户需求展开的。
EN: No successful project is self-oriented; it unfolds around user needs.

ZH: 他的写作风格很导向于浪漫主义。
EN: His writing style is very oriented towards romanticism.

